          class="hover:underline md:inline-block text-center"
          href={address}
          target="_blank"
          title="See on map">238 Thomas St, Dandenong</a
        >
      </div>
      <p class="max-w-[600px] mx-auto text-center text-2xl font-medium">
        Maximize your money's worth with our unbeatable currency exchange rates
